text: Champdor-Corcelles is a commune in the Ain department of eastern France. It was established on 1 January 2016. It is made of the former communes of Champdor and Corcelles.Arrêté préfectoral 27 November 2015 == Related pages == *Communes of the Ain department == References == Category:2016 establishments in France
title: Champdor-Corcelles
